data.description: Exclusive gated community! Waterfront living, where dreams are brought to life amidst the beauty and the serenity of Rivella Island. Here, you have the unique opportunity to build your custom dream home, perfectly tailored to your desires and surrounded by the awe-inspiring splendor of the waterfront.With ocean access right at your doorstep, you can indulge in a variety of water-based activities. Take your yacht or sailboat out for a leisurely cruise, embark on exciting fishing expeditions, or simply relax on your private dock. When it comes to building your custom dream home, the possibilities are endless. Work with architects and designers who specialize and create custom homes. Incorporate large windows and open floor plans to seamlessly blend the indoor and outdoor spaces. Home to be built by custom home builder Atlantic Crest Homes. Voted number one builder Palm Beach County 2020. A developer fee will apply. Site survey and soil test results available. Min. Build 3000 living sq ft. Photos of homes are for illustration purposes. Construction of home is separate from lot purchase. Pricing depends on model and features selected.
